reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just what I needed
reviews.reviewText: I needed a new small table lamp, this one filled that need perfectly. With the 6w led bulb, and full dimming capability, it provides the right light at the right time. Plus there are 2 USB ports fir charging a phone, or other devices. The price was reasonable and delivery was within 3 days. What more could I ask for?

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great lamp for the price - but location matters
reviews.reviewText: Right off I have to say this is a pretty darn nice lamp. It isn't overwhelmingly large, the materials seem to be of good quality and it doesn't have a "cheap" feel to it. The glass dome is solid and thick. The metal doesn't have any visible defects in form or finish. The two USB ports are a nice plus as well and the dimmable rotating switch is nice and smooth.One thing to bear in mind however is that when you use the included lightbulb, the light goes everywhere - the dome is obviously not a shade. So if you're using this on an end table or the like, it throws light across the area. I put this on a desk and found the light coming from the side to reflect on my computer screen and shine in my eyes. Dimming would help but then it was hard to see what I was working on. So my remedy was to replace the included "edison" style bulb with a dimmable can light bulb. This did detract a bit from the lamp's retro appearance but it does a great job directing the light down while still allowing dimmability. Certainly not a dealbreaker and if my desk was bigger I would not hesitate to get a second lamp to complement the first. I will likely get the matching floor lamp though to round everything out.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 10, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Super Fast Set up.
reviews.reviewText: I adore this lamp. I first purchased a touch lamp from another company and it would randomly turn on or off. I wanted the same look but I wanted to be able to control off and on. I bought this lamp due to that capability and the fact that it has two charging ports. I didn't realize when buying this how much I would enjoy the dimmability of the lamp.. This lamp sits on my bed side table and is perfect for a small amount of light as you are waking up or starting to go to sleep, or even more light if you are up reading in bed like I am. The convinence of the two USB charging ports are awesome. I charge my watch and my phone at the same time. All in all it was a great purchase and super easy to put together. If you are into this industrial style I would suggest this lamp. It sure fits with my decor and didn't break the bank.
